********************************************************************************
*                                                                              *
*                 README file for PeLa::Foundation                             *
*                                                                              *
********************************************************************************

This directory contains the PeLa::Foundation release.

What's inside :

README             - this file

build              - build directory for Unit tests for PeLa::Foundation
doc/Doxygen        - Doxygen configuration file for generated documentation 
src/Event          - implementation PeLa::Event::Event class (event appears as C#)
src/Exception      - implementation PeLa::Exception::Exception class (extension of
                     std::exception which includes file name, line number and
                     function name)
src/ExSTl          - implementation PeLa::ExSTL::make_{stl_container} functions
                     (generate stl conteiners (list, vector, queue, priority_queue,
                     set, multiset, map, multimap, stack) by one row)
test/test-*        - Unit tests files for PeLa::Foundation components
test/externals     - externals lib (gmock: http://code.google.com/p/googlemock)
test/unittest.cpp  - main for Unit tests


